snippet.title: Di Gi Charat Fantasy Excellent OP「Welcome!2000」
snippet.description:
Opening movie of Di Gi Charat Fantasy Excellent on the PlayStation 2. This version of the song is slightly different. 

Lyrics: Koge-Donbo
Composition: Yusuke Sakamoto
Vocals: Asami Sanada
